Class AirlinerTechData

  • java.lang.Object
    • by.zyablov.airlinecompany.beans.techdata.AirlinerTechData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UniqueAircraftTechDataBehavior, java.io.Serializable

    public class AirlinerTechData
extends java.lang.Object
implements UniqueAircraftTechDataBehavior, java.io.Serializable
    Class AirlinerTechData represents a unique technical information for AirlinerAircraft class such as airliner type depending on the flight distance and opportunity to have business class on board of an aircraft.

    Class AirlinerTechData implements UniqueAircraftTechDataBehavior to show that's AirlinerAircraft can have such unique technical information.
